highlights.description: LVN conversations are supposed to be like we bumped into each other at the coffee shop
I like getting on a bus and 20 min later arriving at the Overture
Alcohol is too much a part of everything here
I taught at East High for 4 years and I never saw any violence
We talk about inequality but we don't talk about actually integrating neighborhoods
Officials should not just listen to those who have enough money to advocate for themselves
Enjoyed that this was a group of people who did not know one another

title: RLL Event Drop-in Conversation - Madison, WI 117
